description: This Chainlink VRF common Cooter purrs with a rating of 21, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 63, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Stringalong for East, 3 for South, and Stringalong for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90213-17372-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [63 Votes, Common]
